- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a possible category as the paper deals with the semantics of a formal language (Petri nets).
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is a possible category as the paper deals with the formalism of Petri nets and their properties.
- cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) is a possible category as the paper deals with combinatorial arguments and their application to the analysis of Petri nets.
